<meta name="description" content="Attention: This is not intended for emergency situations. If your life or property is at risk, please call 911.Any person who believes that they have been subject to unequal treatment or discrimination by a Clackamas County employee, contractor, or subcontractor has the right to file a complaint against Clackamas County. This form is intended for members of the public. If you are a Clackamas County employee filing a complaint about a work-related matter, please contact your HR representative." />
